insert into public.cards (id, name, arcana, suit, number, image_path, upright_meaning, reversed_meaning, keywords, flower_species) values
  (0, 'The Fool', 'major', NULL, 0, 'major/00-fool.jpg', 'You stand at the edge of something beautifully unknown, held by pure potential. Trust the leap — the universe has never let a genuine beginning fall without a net. This is the moment to begin without needing all the answers.', 'Hesitation is a visitor, not a permanent resident. You may be holding yourself back from a start that is overdue, or rushing blindly past warnings worth heeding. Pause, breathe, and listen to the difference.', '{beginnings,innocence,spontaneity,adventure,potential}', 'dandelion'),
  (1, 'The Magician', 'major', NULL, 1, 'major/01-magician.jpg', 'Every tool you need is already in your hands. Your will, aligned with intention and action, becomes a real and powerful force in the world. This is your moment to make something from nothing.', 'There is a gap between your intentions and your actions, and it is costing you. Check whether you are using your gifts honestly, or spinning wheels of cleverness that lead nowhere real.', '{willpower,skill,manifestation,resourcefulness,concentration}', 'white orchid'),
  (2, 'The High Priestess', 'major', NULL, 2, 'major/02-high-priestess.jpg', 'Beneath the surface of what you can see, a deeper knowing already exists. Be still enough to hear it. The answers you seek are not outside you — they live in the quiet beneath the noise.', 'You may be ignoring your intuition in favour of what looks logical, or secrets are being kept that distort your picture. Come back to your inner compass before moving forward.', '{intuition,mystery,inner knowing,subconscious,stillness}', 'moonflower'),
  (3, 'The Empress', 'major', NULL, 3, 'major/03-empress.jpg', 'Abundance is not something you must chase — it grows from the ground you tend with love. Creativity, beauty, and nurturing belong to you now. Let yourself receive as freely as you give.', 'Something is blocking the natural flow of creation or care — either overgiving, neglect, or a creative block that needs gentle acknowledgement. Restore the balance between tending others and tending yourself.', '{abundance,fertility,nurturing,beauty,nature}', 'rose'),
  (4, 'The Emperor', 'major', NULL, 4, 'major/04-emperor.jpg', 'Stability and structure are not constraints — they are the foundations that let everything else flourish. Authority, discipline, and clear boundaries are your strengths in this moment. Lead with steady hands.', 'Rigidity may be mistaken for strength, or authority may have become control that stifles rather than protects. Ask whether the structure you are holding is serving life or suppressing it.', '{authority,structure,stability,discipline,leadership}', 'thistle'),
  (5, 'The Hierophant', 'major', NULL, 5, 'major/05-hierophant.jpg', 'Tradition and guidance hold real wisdom when approached with an open heart. A teacher, institution, or time-honoured path is offering you something genuine. Receive the teaching before you rewrite it.', 'Conventional wisdom may be chafing against your lived experience, or you may be bending rules at a cost not yet visible. Question tradition thoughtfully, not just rebelliously.', '{tradition,guidance,spirituality,conformity,institutions}', 'lavender'),
  (6, 'The Lovers', 'major', NULL, 6, 'major/06-lovers.jpg', 'At the heart of this is a real choice — one that asks who you are and what you truly value. Love, connection, and alignment are present. The decision before you is not just practical; it is about your whole self.', 'Misalignment is present — in values, in a relationship, or in a choice being made from fear or avoidance rather than genuine love. Clarity about what you believe must come before the next step.', '{love,union,values,alignment,choice}', 'red tulip'),
  (7, 'The Chariot', 'major', NULL, 7, 'major/07-chariot.jpg', 'Victory is not the absence of opposition — it is what happens when you hold opposing forces in disciplined alignment. Your will is strong enough to steer through whatever stands in your way. Drive forward.', 'Control is slipping, or you may be forcing a direction through aggression rather than intention. The tension here is real; it needs acknowledgement before it can be resolved.', '{determination,control,victory,willpower,direction}', 'gladiolus'),
  (8, 'Strength', 'major', NULL, 8, 'major/08-strength.jpg', 'True strength is quiet and patient — it tames the wild without breaking it. You have more power than force could ever demonstrate. Lead from gentleness and watch what opens.', 'Self-doubt or raw emotion may be louder than your quieter knowing right now. Insecurity dressed as strength can do damage. Return to the soft authority that lives beneath the noise.', '{courage,patience,compassion,inner strength,influence}', 'sunflower'),
  (9, 'The Hermit', 'major', NULL, 9, 'major/09-hermit.jpg', 'The light you carry is not just for you — withdrawal and reflection have prepared you to guide others through their own darkness. This is a time for solitude, wisdom, and the kind of knowing that only silence produces.', 'Isolation may have crossed from necessary into lonely, or a return to the world is being avoided. The lamp has been lit — consider whether it is time to bring it back among people.', '{solitude,wisdom,introspection,guidance,withdrawal}', 'white sage'),
  (10, 'Wheel of Fortune', 'major', NULL, 10, 'major/10-wheel-of-fortune.jpg', 'The wheel is turning, and fortune is moving in your favour. Change is inevitable and this cycle is arriving right on time. Trust the larger pattern even when you can only see one spoke.', 'The wheel turns but you may be resisting its motion, or bad luck feels entirely personal when it isn''t. Release what you can''t control; your real task is how you meet the turn.', '{fate,cycles,luck,turning point,destiny}', 'marigold'),
  (11, 'Justice', 'major', NULL, 11, 'major/11-justice.jpg', 'Cause and consequence are in clear alignment here. What is fair will be seen; what is true will emerge. Act with integrity and you will have nothing to fear from what the scales reveal.', 'Something is out of balance — dishonesty, unfair treatment, or avoiding accountability in yourself or others. The scale will eventually settle; better to face it honestly now.', '{fairness,truth,cause and effect,law,accountability}', 'white lily'),
  (12, 'The Hanged Man', 'major', NULL, 12, 'major/12-hanged-man.jpg', 'Surrender here is not defeat — it is the choice to see from a completely different angle. What looks like a pause is actually a profound reorientation. Let yourself hang in the in-between; the view is worth it.', 'The resistance to letting go is costing more than the letting go would. Sacrifice is being avoided, or the pause has become stagnation. Consider what you are unwilling to release and why.', '{surrender,new perspective,pause,sacrifice,suspension}', 'lotus'),
  (13, 'Death', 'major', NULL, 13, 'major/13-death.jpg', 'This is not an ending — it is the clearing that makes space for what is actually meant to grow. Something is completing, and the transformation it offers is real and necessary. Let it pass with dignity.', 'A necessary change is being resisted, prolonging something that has already run its course. The fear of ending may be keeping you in something that no longer serves life. Grief is allowed; so is letting go.', '{transformation,endings,transition,change,release}', 'black-eyed susan'),
  (14, 'Temperance', 'major', NULL, 14, 'major/14-temperance.jpg', 'The art of blending — patience, moderation, and the long view — is your superpower right now. There is a middle path that holds beauty and balance. You are being invited to flow between extremes rather than choose one.', 'Excess or imbalance is present, or you are trying to force things that need time to merge naturally. Impatience here costs more than waiting. Return to the practice of gentle, steady integration.', '{balance,moderation,patience,integration,flow}', 'iris'),
  (15, 'The Devil', 'major', NULL, 15, 'major/15-devil.jpg', 'The chains you see are not as fixed as they appear. What binds you is, in part, a story you keep choosing. Acknowledging the patterns of addiction, materialism, or unhealthy attachment is the first real step toward freedom.', 'You are beginning to see through the illusion that held you. Breaking free from something — a habit, a relationship, a belief — is genuinely possible now. Don''t go back to what you''ve started to outgrow.', '{bondage,shadow,addiction,materialism,patterns}', 'nightshade'),
  (16, 'The Tower', 'major', NULL, 16, 'major/16-tower.jpg', 'What is built on false foundations must eventually fall — and this clearing, however jarring, is ultimately freeing. The shock is real; so is the ground that was always beneath it. Rebuild from what is true.', 'Disaster is being avoided or delayed, but at what cost? Or perhaps the worst has already passed and you are still bracing for an impact that has come and gone. The tower has fallen; it is safe to look up.', '{upheaval,revelation,chaos,breaking down,liberation}', 'bird of paradise'),
  (17, 'The Star', 'major', NULL, 17, 'major/17-star.jpg', 'After the storm, hope arrives quietly and without conditions. Healing is already happening, even where you can''t see it. Let yourself be held by the possibility that things genuinely can get better.', 'Despair or hopelessness is dimming your view of what is still possible. Faith in the future may feel naive, but its absence is costing you more. Even a small point of light can be followed.', '{hope,renewal,healing,inspiration,serenity}', 'morning glory'),
  (18, 'The Moon', 'major', NULL, 18, 'major/18-moon.jpg', 'The path ahead is illuminated only partially — and that is the nature of this passage. Illusion, intuition, and the unconscious are all speaking at once. Feel your way forward rather than demanding certainty.', 'Confusion is starting to lift, or fears that seemed enormous are shrinking in the daylight. Deception — from yourself or others — may be becoming clear. You are finding your footing.', '{illusion,fear,the unconscious,confusion,intuition}', 'night-blooming cereus'),
  (19, 'The Sun', 'major', NULL, 19, 'major/19-sun.jpg', 'Joy, clarity, and vitality are flowing toward you now. This is a time of genuine warmth, success, and the simple pleasure of being alive and in the light. Let yourself enjoy it without reservation.', 'Joy is being blocked — by pessimism, overconfidence, or a temporary cloud that feels permanent. The sun is still there; let yourself move toward whatever light is available right now.', '{joy,vitality,success,clarity,warmth}', 'sunflower'),
  (20, 'Judgement', 'major', NULL, 20, 'major/20-judgement.jpg', 'A call is rising within you — to rise, to answer, to step into a renewed version of who you are. This is a moment of reckoning and rebirth. What you have been through has prepared you for this.', 'Doubt or self-judgement is muffling the call. You may be refusing to forgive yourself or others, which makes it impossible to move forward. Hear the summons; even an imperfect answer is still an answer.', '{rebirth,absolution,reflection,awakening,reckoning}', 'trumpet lily'),
  (21, 'The World', 'major', NULL, 21, 'major/21-world.jpg', 'You have arrived. A cycle has completed with wholeness and the kind of satisfaction that can only come from genuine effort. Celebrate this; let it land fully before you leap into the next thing.', 'Completion is close but not quite reached — something is being rushed or a loose end is being avoided. Take the last steps with the same care you brought to the beginning.', '{completion,wholeness,integration,achievement,travel}', 'peony'),
  (22, 'Ace of Wands', 'minor', 'wands', 1, 'minor/wands/01-ace.jpg', 'A new creative spark is igniting — raw, full of possibility, and asking to be channelled into something real. Say yes to the beginning before the whole picture is clear. Fire starts with a single point of light.', 'Creative energy is stalled or scattered. A new idea hasn''t quite caught, or excitement has burned out before finding form. Reconnect with what genuinely moves you before trying to begin.', '{inspiration,new venture,creative spark,potential,enthusiasm}', 'flame lily'),
  (23, 'Two of Wands', 'minor', 'wands', 2, 'minor/wands/02-two.jpg', 'You are standing at the threshold of a larger world, planning and considering the territory ahead. Your vision has outgrown your current container. Begin mapping the future you''re ready to step into.', 'Plans feel stuck or a fear of the unknown is keeping you from expanding. The horizon is there; the hesitation is only in how you''re holding the decision, not in the decision itself.', '{planning,vision,partnership,discovery,expansion}', 'bird of paradise'),
  (24, 'Three of Wands', 'minor', 'wands', 3, 'minor/wands/03-three.jpg', 'What you set in motion is already beginning to come back to you. Ships are on their way. Expand your vision further — this is the moment to look beyond the immediate and grow into what is arriving.', 'Plans are returning with complications, or expansion feels blocked by circumstances outside your control. Be patient with the timing; delays are not failures, just adjustments.', '{foresight,progress,expansion,enterprise,results}', 'orange blossom'),
  (25, 'Four of Wands', 'minor', 'wands', 4, 'minor/wands/04-four.jpg', 'There is genuine cause for celebration — a milestone reached, a homecoming, a moment of shared joy. Let yourself rest in the warmth of what has been accomplished. Community and stability are present.', 'Celebration feels hollow, or instability is disrupting what should be a moment of rest. A transition or conflict in community may need attention before real joy can land.', '{celebration,community,harmony,homecoming,stability}', 'peach blossom'),
  (26, 'Five of Wands', 'minor', 'wands', 5, 'minor/wands/05-five.jpg', 'Conflict and competition are present, but this friction is generative if you can hold your ground without losing sight of the bigger picture. Challenge strengthens what survives it.', 'Conflict is ending, or internal conflict is what needs resolution. Tension that has no outlet becomes stagnation. Find a constructive channel for the energy.', '{conflict,competition,tension,chaos,disagreement}', 'thistle'),
  (27, 'Six of Wands', 'minor', 'wands', 6, 'minor/wands/06-six.jpg', 'Recognition, victory, and public acknowledgement are arriving. Your efforts have been seen. Accept the moment of success with grace rather than deflecting — you earned it.', 'Ego may be inflated, or recognition is being sought more than deserved. Or perhaps success has arrived but feels empty or unearned. Reassess what you are trying to prove and to whom.', '{victory,recognition,leadership,pride,success}', 'yellow tulip'),
  (28, 'Seven of Wands', 'minor', 'wands', 7, 'minor/wands/07-seven.jpg', 'You are defending what you''ve built against pressure from many directions. Hold your position. The challenge is real, but so is what you are standing for. Perseverance is the whole task right now.', 'You may be feeling overwhelmed, or giving up ground that still deserves to be defended. Ask whether the struggle is worth continuing, and be honest about whether retreat is wisdom or exhaustion.', '{perseverance,defense,challenge,resilience,standing firm}', 'agave'),
  (29, 'Eight of Wands', 'minor', 'wands', 8, 'minor/wands/08-eight.jpg', 'Everything is moving fast now — swift action, momentum, and communication all converging at once. Ride the current rather than fighting it. Things are landing right where they need to.', 'Miscommunication or delays are stalling momentum. Energy is scattered or misdirected. Slow down long enough to aim before releasing the arrow.', '{swift action,momentum,news,speed,progress}', 'shooting star'),
  (30, 'Nine of Wands', 'minor', 'wands', 9, 'minor/wands/09-nine.jpg', 'You are battered but still standing. The weariness is real, but so is your resilience. One more push is what is needed — you are closer to the finish than the exhaustion suggests.', 'Stubbornness may be mistaken for perseverance, or you are worn down to a point where rest is the wisest move. Refusing help costs more than asking for it.', '{resilience,persistence,stamina,boundaries,last stand}', 'cactus flower'),
  (31, 'Ten of Wands', 'minor', 'wands', 10, 'minor/wands/10-ten.jpg', 'You are carrying a great deal, and the burden is real. But the destination is close. What you are bearing has purpose — set it down long enough to remember why you picked it up, then continue.', 'The load has become too heavy, or you are carrying responsibility that isn''t yours to carry. Delegating, releasing, or asking for help is not weakness — it is the next right move.', '{burden,responsibility,hard work,completion,exhaustion}', 'heather'),
  (32, 'Page of Wands', 'minor', 'wands', 11, 'minor/wands/11-page.jpg', 'A spark of enthusiastic, adventurous energy is present — yours or someone nearby. This is the energy of free exploration, fresh ideas, and the willingness to try before knowing all the steps. Follow the curiosity.', 'Energy is unfocused or enthusiasm is outrunning commitment. A creative idea needs grounding before it can become anything more than excitement.', '{curiosity,enthusiasm,free spirit,exploration,new ideas}', 'buttercup'),
  (33, 'Knight of Wands', 'minor', 'wands', 12, 'minor/wands/12-knight.jpg', 'Passionate, bold, and fast — this energy moves on instinct and rarely waits for permission. Something exciting is charging forward. The challenge is directing the fire without extinguishing it.', 'Impulsiveness, scattered energy, or a project abandoned before it reached anything. The fire needs a purpose, not just a spark.', '{passion,adventure,impulsiveness,energy,action}', 'red poppy'),
  (34, 'Queen of Wands', 'minor', 'wands', 13, 'minor/wands/13-queen.jpg', 'Vibrant, confident, and generous with her fire — she knows who she is and doesn''t apologise for it. Creative authority and warm leadership are your gifts in this moment. Let them shine without shrinking.', 'Confidence may be tipping into jealousy or dominance, or self-doubt is dimming a light that deserves to be bright. Reclaim your power without needing to dim others''.', '{confidence,warmth,creativity,determination,charisma}', 'dahlia'),
  (35, 'King of Wands', 'minor', 'wands', 14, 'minor/wands/14-king.jpg', 'Bold vision, natural leadership, and the ability to inspire others are yours now. Lead with the fire of genuine conviction and people will follow. Your creative authority is a gift to share.', 'Leadership may have become tyranny, or vision without follow-through is leaving projects unfinished. True authority is earned through consistency, not just declared.', '{vision,leadership,entrepreneurship,boldness,inspiration}', 'king protea'),
  (36, 'Ace of Cups', 'minor', 'cups', 1, 'minor/cups/01-ace.jpg', 'An overflow of love, intuition, and emotional possibility is present. This is the beginning of something tender and real — let your heart be open to receive what is pouring in.', 'Emotional blocks or fear of vulnerability are keeping the cup from filling. Something beautiful is being held at arm''s length. Let yourself feel what is actually there.', '{love,new beginnings,compassion,creativity,intuition}', 'water lily'),
  (37, 'Two of Cups', 'minor', 'cups', 2, 'minor/cups/02-two.jpg', 'A real connection — romantic, creative, or deeply human — is forming or deepening. There is mutual recognition here, an exchange of genuine feeling. This relationship matters.', 'Imbalance or disharmony in a relationship is present. Love may be one-sided, or a break in connection needs to be acknowledged before it widens.', '{union,partnership,attraction,mutual respect,connection}', 'forget-me-not'),
  (38, 'Three of Cups', 'minor', 'cups', 3, 'minor/cups/03-three.jpg', 'Celebration, community, and the joy of being together — raise your cup to what and who you love. This is a time of friendship, abundance shared, and the warmth of belonging.', 'Overindulgence, gossip, or conflict within a group is souring what should be joyful. A celebration feels hollow, or community has become a source of drain rather than nourishment.', '{celebration,friendship,community,abundance,joy}', 'clover'),
  (39, 'Four of Cups', 'minor', 'cups', 4, 'minor/cups/04-four.jpg', 'Contemplation and quiet discontent are inviting a deeper look at what you truly want. Withdraw enough to hear your own desires again — something new is being offered if you look up.', 'Apathy is shifting, or a period of withdrawal is ending. You may be ready to re-engage with life and receive what has been quietly waiting. Look up from the introspection.', '{contemplation,apathy,reevaluation,discontent,introspection}', 'violet'),
  (40, 'Five of Cups', 'minor', 'cups', 5, 'minor/cups/05-five.jpg', 'Grief is real and it deserves space. The loss you are feeling is genuine. But when you are ready, turn — there are cups still standing behind you, full and waiting.', 'You are beginning to turn from grief toward the cups still standing. Acceptance and the willingness to move forward are returning. Be gentle with the pace of your own healing.', '{loss,grief,disappointment,regret,acceptance}', 'forget-me-not'),
  (41, 'Six of Cups', 'minor', 'cups', 6, 'minor/cups/06-six.jpg', 'Nostalgia and the sweetness of the past are visiting. This is a time of returning — to a person, a place, a part of yourself that you had set aside. Let the innocence of it nourish you.', 'Living too much in the past may be preventing real presence. Nostalgia has a sweetness but also a stickiness. Let the memory inform but not replace what is happening now.', '{nostalgia,childhood,reunion,past,innocence}', 'sweet pea'),
  (42, 'Seven of Cups', 'minor', 'cups', 7, 'minor/cups/07-seven.jpg', 'Many paths and possibilities are appearing, some shimmering and some deceptive. Fantasy and imagination are vivid right now. Ground yourself before choosing — not all that glitters is what it appears.', 'Confusion is clearing, or illusion is being seen through at last. You are coming back to what is real and what actually matters. Make choices from clarity, not wishful thinking.', '{illusion,choices,fantasy,temptation,imagination}', 'bluebell'),
  (43, 'Eight of Cups', 'minor', 'cups', 8, 'minor/cups/08-eight.jpg', 'Walking away from something that once mattered, in search of something more meaningful, takes real courage. You are not abandoning; you are answering a deeper call. The journey inward has begun.', 'You may be staying in something long past its time, or leaving prematurely before the real learning has arrived. Ask honestly what you are walking toward, not just what you are leaving.', '{withdrawal,transition,seeking,letting go,new direction}', 'wisteria'),
  (44, 'Nine of Cups', 'minor', 'cups', 9, 'minor/cups/09-nine.jpg', 'The wish card. Satisfaction, fulfilment, and emotional abundance are present — the cups are full and so are you. Allow yourself to feel the pleasure of having what you have.', 'Satisfaction feels hollow, or you are close to contentment but something is still off. Material comfort may have outpaced emotional nourishment. Look beneath the fullness.', '{contentment,satisfaction,wishes,gratitude,abundance}', 'peony'),
  (45, 'Ten of Cups', 'minor', 'cups', 10, 'minor/cups/10-ten.jpg', 'Emotional completion and lasting happiness with those you love. The family or community you have built is real and true. This is what wholeness in the heart looks like.', 'Family or community harmony is strained. Underneath the surface, all may not be as well as it appears. Honest conversations are needed before real peace can return.', '{harmony,happiness,family,completion,belonging}', 'cherry blossom'),
  (46, 'Page of Cups', 'minor', 'cups', 11, 'minor/cups/11-page.jpg', 'A sensitive, imaginative, dreamy energy is present — open to surprise and to the emotional messages arriving from unexpected places. Stay curious about what your feelings are trying to tell you.', 'Emotional immaturity or creative blocks are present. Feelings are being avoided or over-dramatised. Come back to the genuine innocence of what you feel, without performance.', '{curiosity,sensitivity,imagination,messages,new emotions}', 'snowdrop'),
  (47, 'Knight of Cups', 'minor', 'cups', 12, 'minor/cups/12-knight.jpg', 'Romantic, idealistic, and emotionally driven — this energy arrives with feeling and invitation. Someone or something is offering itself with great tenderness. Receive it with an open heart.', 'Moodiness, emotional manipulation, or a romantic idealisation that has lost touch with reality. Feelings need to be honest before they can be acted on with integrity.', '{romance,charm,idealism,following the heart,invitation}', 'anemone'),
  (48, 'Queen of Cups', 'minor', 'cups', 13, 'minor/cups/13-queen.jpg', 'Empathic, emotionally intelligent, and intuitively wise — she feels deeply without being consumed by it. Trust your intuition and bring genuine compassion to those around you and to yourself.', 'Emotions may be overwhelming clarity, or emotional manipulation — conscious or not — is present. Care for others without losing yourself in the process.', '{empathy,intuition,compassion,emotional intelligence,depth}', 'hydrangea'),
  (49, 'King of Cups', 'minor', 'cups', 14, 'minor/cups/14-king.jpg', 'Emotional mastery and wise compassion — he holds feeling and reason together without losing either. Lead and live from a place of genuine emotional intelligence. Your depth is a strength.', 'Emotional suppression or using emotional intelligence for manipulation rather than care. The balance between feeling and control needs recalibrating.', '{emotional mastery,diplomacy,wisdom,calm,compassion}', 'blue lotus'),
  (50, 'Ace of Swords', 'minor', 'swords', 1, 'minor/swords/01-ace.jpg', 'A breakthrough of clarity is arriving — sharp, clean, and a little startling in its truth. The sword cuts through confusion and makes room for what is actually real. Seize this moment of clear seeing.', 'Clarity is blocked, or a truth is known but being avoided. The sword is dull when it needs sharpening, or you are cutting where you should be listening.', '{clarity,breakthrough,truth,intellect,new perspective}', 'iris'),
  (51, 'Two of Swords', 'minor', 'swords', 2, 'minor/swords/02-two.jpg', 'A difficult decision is being held at bay — you are keeping the tension in balance rather than making a move. The blindfold is a choice. When you are ready, look at what the evidence actually says.', 'Indecision is releasing, or information that was hidden is now becoming visible. The stalemate can end. Be willing to see what you''ve been avoiding.', '{indecision,stalemate,avoidance,balance,difficult choice}', 'white magnolia'),
  (52, 'Three of Swords', 'minor', 'swords', 3, 'minor/swords/03-three.jpg', 'Heartbreak and sorrow are present, and they are asking to be felt — not solved, not reasoned away, just met. Grief is honest. Let this pain pass through you rather than around you.', 'Healing from heartbreak is beginning. The wound is real but is slowly closing. Be patient with yourself as you integrate what has happened and begin to feel whole again.', '{heartbreak,grief,sorrow,pain,truth}', 'weeping willow'),
  (53, 'Four of Swords', 'minor', 'swords', 4, 'minor/swords/04-four.jpg', 'Rest is not retreat — it is the thing that makes everything else possible. You are in a period of recovery and contemplation. Give your mind and body the quiet they are asking for.', 'Rest is ending, or an inability to rest is taking its toll. Return to stillness if you have rushed back too soon, or begin to re-engage gently if the pause has served its purpose.', '{rest,recovery,retreat,contemplation,stillness}', 'lavender'),
  (54, 'Five of Swords', 'minor', 'swords', 5, 'minor/swords/05-five.jpg', 'A conflict has been won, but at a cost worth examining. Victory that requires dishonesty or leaves others diminished is a hollow one. Consider what kind of winner you want to be.', 'Conflict is ending and reconciliation is possible. Or the damage from a dishonest win is becoming apparent. It is not too late to choose integrity over advantage.', '{conflict,defeat,hollow victory,tension,self-interest}', 'blackthorn'),
  (55, 'Six of Swords', 'minor', 'swords', 6, 'minor/swords/06-six.jpg', 'Moving away from turmoil toward calmer water — the journey is gentle but the grief of leaving is real. You are being carried toward something better. Let the movement happen.', 'Transition is resisted, or you feel unable to move on even when the way forward is clear. Stagnation is a kind of suffering. The boat is waiting.', '{transition,moving on,release,travel,calmer waters}', 'sea lavender'),
  (56, 'Seven of Swords', 'minor', 'swords', 7, 'minor/swords/07-seven.jpg', 'Strategy, cunning, and the wisdom to know when to move carefully rather than directly are called for. Sometimes the bold move is to act quietly. Be aware of deception — in others and in yourself.', 'Deception is being uncovered, or you are second-guessing a strategic retreat that was actually wise. Hidden things are coming to light. Honesty now costs less than it will later.', '{deception,strategy,cunning,stealth,getting away with it}', 'foxglove'),
  (57, 'Eight of Swords', 'minor', 'swords', 8, 'minor/swords/08-eight.jpg', 'You feel trapped, but the restraints are largely held in place by the way you are thinking about your situation. The cage door is not fully latched. Question the beliefs that are keeping you stuck.', 'Freedom is within reach, or you are recognising that the prison was a mental one. A limiting belief is releasing. Take the first small step out of the story that has held you.', '{restriction,trapped,negative thinking,victimhood,fear}', 'bindweed'),
  (58, 'Nine of Swords', 'minor', 'swords', 9, 'minor/swords/09-nine.jpg', 'Anxiety, nightmares, and worry are present — the kind that arrive at three in the morning. The fear feels total but it is not. You are not alone in this, and the light does return.', 'Anxiety is beginning to ease, or the worst-case scenario is proving less catastrophic than the mind made it. Healing from mental anguish is slow but real. Be patient with yourself.', '{anxiety,worry,nightmares,anguish,despair}', 'monkshood'),
  (59, 'Ten of Swords', 'minor', 'swords', 10, 'minor/swords/10-ten.jpg', 'A painful ending — abrupt, final, hard. But look: the dawn is already beginning in the distance. This is the rock bottom that is also the turning point. What comes next is truly new.', 'The worst is passing, or you are resisting the full reality of an ending that needs to be acknowledged before you can rise. The swords are out. The next step is standing up.', '{painful ending,betrayal,crisis,rock bottom,new dawn}', 'nightshade'),
  (60, 'Page of Swords', 'minor', 'swords', 11, 'minor/swords/11-page.jpg', 'Alert, curious, and quick — this energy is watching, gathering information, and not yet committing to action. Stay sharp and be careful about speaking before you have thought things through.', 'Gossip, careless words, or immaturity in how information is being handled. The tongue moves before the mind. Be more intentional with what you say and to whom.', '{curiosity,intellect,watchfulness,communication,restlessness}', 'meadow sage'),
  (61, 'Knight of Swords', 'minor', 'swords', 12, 'minor/swords/12-knight.jpg', 'Rapid, driven, and sharp — this knight charges at the truth without hesitation. Ambition and intellect are fully engaged. The challenge is ensuring the direction is right before the charge begins.', 'Aggression, recklessness, or the sword used for destruction rather than clarity. Slow down. Not every battle needs to be fought at full gallop.', '{ambition,action,direct,fast-paced,driven}', 'yarrow'),
  (62, 'Queen of Swords', 'minor', 'swords', 13, 'minor/swords/13-queen.jpg', 'Clear-eyed, honest, and unbothered by sentimentality — she sees what is true and names it with precision. Bring the same clarity and direct communication to your current situation. Truth delivered with care is a gift.', 'Coldness, cruelty, or using intelligence to wound rather than illuminate. Bitterness may be colouring perception. Clarity without compassion is just sharpness.', '{clarity,honesty,independence,directness,wisdom}', 'snowdrop'),
  (63, 'King of Swords', 'minor', 'swords', 14, 'minor/swords/14-king.jpg', 'Intellectual authority, clear judgment, and the ability to hold complexity without collapsing it into something simpler than it is. Think with discipline and lead with clarity.', 'Intellectual arrogance, manipulation through language, or power used to confuse rather than clarify. Check that the sharp mind is in service of truth.', '{authority,truth,clarity,intellectual power,ethics}', 'agapanthus'),
  (64, 'Ace of Pentacles', 'minor', 'pentacles', 1, 'minor/pentacles/01-ace.jpg', 'A tangible new beginning — in finances, in the body, in the material world. Something real and solid is being offered. Receive it with both hands and plant it where it can grow.', 'Missed opportunity or poor financial judgment. A material beginning is being squandered or has been lost to poor timing. Tend more carefully to the ground beneath your feet.', '{new opportunity,abundance,prosperity,security,practical beginnings}', 'daffodil'),
  (65, 'Two of Pentacles', 'minor', 'pentacles', 2, 'minor/pentacles/02-two.jpg', 'You are juggling multiple priorities and managing it more gracefully than it may feel from the inside. Adaptability and balance are your skills right now. Keep the rhythm going.', 'The juggle is becoming unsustainable. Something is about to drop, or is already dropping. Reprioritise before the balance collapses entirely.', '{balance,adaptability,time management,priorities,juggling}', 'sweet alyssum'),
  (66, 'Three of Pentacles', 'minor', 'pentacles', 3, 'minor/pentacles/03-three.jpg', 'Collaboration, craftsmanship, and the reward of learning from those who know more. Good work done together is more than the sum of its parts. Value the team and the process.', 'Conflict in teamwork, poor planning, or the lack of recognition for contribution. Consider whether collaboration is actually happening or whether it has become something else.', '{teamwork,craftsmanship,learning,collaboration,skill}', 'edelweiss'),
  (67, 'Four of Pentacles', 'minor', 'pentacles', 4, 'minor/pentacles/04-four.jpg', 'Security and stability are valuable — hold what you have worked for. But check whether protection has crossed into hoarding, or whether control is keeping out more than just threats.', 'Greed or excessive control is costing more than it is protecting. A release of financial or emotional hoarding would allow real abundance to flow in.', '{security,control,stability,conservatism,holding on}', 'bay laurel'),
  (68, 'Five of Pentacles', 'minor', 'pentacles', 5, 'minor/pentacles/05-five.jpg', 'Financial difficulty or a sense of isolation in the cold are present. The warmth and support nearby may be easier to reach than it feels. You are not as alone as the wind would have you believe.', 'Recovery from hardship is beginning. The worst of the financial or emotional cold is passing. Open to the help that is within reach and let yourself come in from the cold.', '{hardship,poverty,isolation,struggle,recovery}', 'snowdrop'),
  (69, 'Six of Pentacles', 'minor', 'pentacles', 6, 'minor/pentacles/06-six.jpg', 'Generosity, charity, and the fair distribution of what you have — whether you are giving or receiving, the exchange is real. Both positions carry their own dignity.', 'Imbalance in giving and receiving — strings attached, gifts used as power, or receiving from a place of dependence rather than genuine need. Look at what generosity is really costing.', '{generosity,charity,sharing,balance,giving and receiving}', 'cosmos'),
  (70, 'Seven of Pentacles', 'minor', 'pentacles', 7, 'minor/pentacles/07-seven.jpg', 'You have put in the work and now you pause to assess the harvest. This is a moment for reflection on whether what is growing is what you intended to grow. Long-term investment is paying off.', 'Impatience with slow growth, or effort that is not producing the expected yield. Step back and ask whether the strategy needs adjusting, or whether more time is simply needed.', '{patience,assessment,long-term vision,harvest,investment}', 'sunflower'),
  (71, 'Eight of Pentacles', 'minor', 'pentacles', 8, 'minor/pentacles/08-eight.jpg', 'Diligence, craft, and the mastery that comes from showing up again and again. You are becoming good at something through genuine, unhurried effort. Trust the process of apprenticeship.', 'Perfectionism, monotony, or a lack of attention to quality. The work is being done but not with care. Ask whether you are phoning it in or burning yourself out with the impossible standard.', '{diligence,mastery,craft,skill,dedication}', 'chamomile'),
  (72, 'Nine of Pentacles', 'minor', 'pentacles', 9, 'minor/pentacles/09-nine.jpg', 'Self-sufficiency, elegance, and the quiet satisfaction of what you have built entirely through your own effort. This is abundance earned and grace well-deserved. Enjoy it without apology.', 'Dependence on external validation or material security that masks inner emptiness. The lifestyle looks beautiful but something important is missing. What is it you actually need?', '{self-sufficiency,luxury,independence,refinement,earned abundance}', 'gardenia'),
  (73, 'Ten of Pentacles', 'minor', 'pentacles', 10, 'minor/pentacles/10-ten.jpg', 'Legacy, wealth passed down, and the enduring prosperity of what you have built across time. Family, heritage, and the satisfaction of long-term security — all are present here.', 'Family conflict over money or inheritance, or a legacy that has become a burden rather than a gift. Reexamine what you truly want to carry and what to release.', '{legacy,wealth,family,security,long-term success}', 'wisteria'),
  (74, 'Page of Pentacles', 'minor', 'pentacles', 11, 'minor/pentacles/11-page.jpg', 'A grounded, studious, and practical energy is present. A new skill or financial venture is being explored with genuine curiosity and care. Take the time to learn before you invest.', 'Procrastination, lack of focus, or a practical endeavour that has not got off the ground due to dreaminess or laziness. Get specific and start small.', '{opportunity,study,groundedness,new skills,practical curiosity}', 'clover'),
  (75, 'Knight of Pentacles', 'minor', 'pentacles', 12, 'minor/pentacles/12-knight.jpg', 'Methodical, dependable, and unhurried — this knight gets there through patience and consistent effort rather than speed or flash. Honour the routine; it is building something real.', 'Stagnation, stubbornness, or a dull routine that has become its own kind of trap. Progress requires some flexibility. Consider whether the method is serving the goal or has become the goal.', '{routine,dependability,patience,thoroughness,groundedness}', 'fern'),
  (76, 'Queen of Pentacles', 'minor', 'pentacles', 13, 'minor/pentacles/13-queen.jpg', 'Nurturing, practical, and abundantly generous — she creates a home wherever she goes, in the fullest sense of the word. Tend your material and domestic life with the same care you give to others.', 'Smothering, financial dependency, or the neglect of self in over-tending others. Reassess the balance between care for others and honest care for yourself.', '{nurturing,practicality,abundance,home,security}', 'foxglove'),
  (77, 'King of Pentacles', 'minor', 'pentacles', 14, 'minor/pentacles/14-king.jpg', 'Material mastery, reliable leadership, and the quiet power of someone who has built something lasting through steady effort and integrity. Wealth here is not just financial — it is a way of being.', 'Materialism, stubbornness, or a fixation on security that has become its own limitation. Power used without care. Consider whether what you''ve built is actually making life richer.', '{wealth,stability,leadership,security,ambition}', 'oak')
